(38, 7, 'assets/upload/images/news/02.jpg', 'thong-bao-thay-doi-thong-tin-visa-du-hoc-han-quoc-2016', 'Thông báo thay đổi thông tin visa du học Hàn Quốc năm 2016', ' ', 'Thông tin Visa', NULL, 'THÔNG BÁO MỚI NHẤT VỀ HỒ SƠ XIN VISA DU HỌC HÀN QUỐC', NULL, '<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD HTML 4.0 Transitional//EN" "http://www.w3.org/TR/REC-html40/loose.dtd">\n<html><body><h3 align="center" style="margin-top:0in;text-align:center;line-height:150%"></h3><p style="margin:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:\r\ninter-ideograph;line-height:150%"><span style=''font-size:13.0pt;line-height:\r\n150%;font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";color:#1D2129''>V&agrave;o ng&agrave;y 12/05/2016, &#272;&#7841;i\r\ns&#7913; qu&aacute;n H&agrave;n Qu&#7889;c &#273;&atilde; ra th&ocirc;ng b&aacute;o trong &#273;&oacute; l&#432;u &yacute; khi xin visa du h&#7885;c nh&#432; sau:</span><p></p></p><p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; line-height: 150%;"><span style=''font-size:13.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";\r\ncolor:#1D2129''>- &#7842;nh tr&ecirc;n t&#7901; khai xin c&#7845;p visa ph&#7843;i ch&#7909;p trong v&ograve;ng 06 th&aacute;ng\r\ntr&#432;&#7899;c ng&agrave;y n&#7897;p h&#7891; s&#417;. Tr&#432;&#7901;ng h&#7907;p &#7843;nh d&aacute;n tr&ecirc;n t&#7901; khai xin c&#7845;p visa kh&aacute;c v&#7899;i\r\nng&#432;&#7901;i ph&#7887;ng v&#7845;n th&igrave; h&#7891; s&#417; c&oacute; th&#7875; b&#7883; t&#7915; ch&#7889;i visa.<p></p></span></p><p style="margin:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:\r\ninter-ideograph;line-height:150%"><span class="textexposedshow"><span style=''font-size:13.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";\r\ncolor:#1D2129''>- C&aacute;c b&#7897; h&#7891; s&#417; xin visa du h&#7885;c c&oacute; hi&#7879;u l&#7921;c trong v&ograve;ng 3 th&aacute;ng t&#7915;\r\nng&agrave;y c&#7845;p (tr&#7915; c&aacute;c lo&#7841;i gi&#7845;y t&#7901; g&#7889;c nh&#432; b&#7857;ng t&#7889;t nghi&#7879;p, ch&#7913;ng ch&#7881;, b&#7843;ng &#273;i&#7875;m).<p></p></span></span></p><p style="margin:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:\r\ninter-ideograph;line-height:150%"><span class="textexposedshow"><span style=''font-size:13.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";\r\ncolor:#1D2129''>- Gi&#7845;y x&aacute;c nh&#7853;n s&#7889; d&#432; t&agrave;i kho&#7843;n th&igrave; c&oacute; hi&#7879;u l&#7921;c trong v&ograve;ng 10\r\nng&agrave;y t&#7915; ng&agrave;y c&#7845;p.<p></p></span></span></p><p style="margin:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:\r\ninter-ideograph;line-height:150%"><span class="textexposedshow"><span style=''font-size:13.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";\r\ncolor:#1D2129''>- B&#7843;n d&#7883;ch c&ocirc;ng ch&#7913;ng ph&#7843;i c&ocirc;ng ch&#7913;ng t&#7915; b&#7843;n g&#7889;c. Tr&#432;&#7901;ng h&#7907;p\r\nch&#7909;p &#7843;nh b&#7843;n g&#7889;c v&agrave; d&#7883;ch c&ocirc;ng ch&#7913;ng, kh&ocirc;ng ch&#7845;p nh&#7853;n h&#7891; s&#417;.<p></p></span></span></p><p style="margin:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:\r\ninter-ideograph;line-height:150%"><span class="textexposedshow"><span style=''font-size:13.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";\r\ncolor:#1D2129''>- Gi&#7845;y nh&#7853;p h&#7885;c do nh&agrave; tr&#432;&#7901;ng H&agrave;n Qu&#7889;c c&#7845;p c&oacute; hi&#7879;u l&#7921;c trong\r\nv&ograve;ng 3 th&aacute;ng t&#7915; ng&agrave;y c&#7845;p.<p></p></span></span></p><p style="margin:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:\r\ninter-ideograph;line-height:150%"><span class="textexposedshow"><span style=''font-size:13.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";\r\ncolor:#1D2129''>- T&#259;ng c&#432;&#7901;ng th&#7849;m tra v&#7873; vi&#7879;c thay &#273;&#7893;i &#273;&#7883;a ch&#7881;:<p></p></span></span></p><p style="margin:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:\r\ninter-ideograph;line-height:150%"><span class="textexposedshow"><span style=''font-size:13.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";\r\ncolor:#1D2129''>+ &#272;&#7889;i v&#7899;i tr&#432;&#7901;ng h&#7907;p xin visa h&#7885;c ti&#7871;ng (D-4-1), v&#7873; nguy&ecirc;n t&#7855;c\r\ns&#7869; t&#7915; ch&#7889;i visa &#273;&#7889;i v&#7899;i c&aacute;c tr&#432;&#7901;ng h&#7907;p chuy&#7875;n h&#7897; kh&#7849;u v&#7873; khu v&#7921;c thu&#7897;c qu&#7843;n l&yacute;\r\nc&#7911;a &#272;&#7841;i s&#7913; qu&aacute;n sau khi t&#7889;t nghi&#7879;p THPT.<p></p></span></span></p><p style="margin:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:\r\ninter-ideograph;line-height:150%"><span class="textexposedshow"><span style=''font-size:13.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";\r\ncolor:#1D2129''>+ Ph&#7843;i xin visa t&#7841;i khu v&#7921;c n&#417;i t&#7889;t nghi&#7879;p THPT.<p></p></span></span></p><p style="margin:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:\r\ninter-ideograph;line-height:150%"><span class="textexposedshow"><span style=''font-size:13.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";\r\ncolor:#1D2129''>Tuy nhi&ecirc;n, c&oacute; th&#7875; xem x&eacute;t c&#7845;p visa sau khi x&aacute;c minh v&#7899;i ch&iacute;nh\r\nquy&#7873;n s&#7903; t&#7841;i v&agrave; tr&#432;&#7901;ng h&#7885;c &#273;&#7889;i v&#7899;i nh&#7919;ng ng&#432;&#7901;i &#273;&atilde; chuy&#7875;n h&#7897; kh&#7849;u tr&ecirc;n 01 n&#259;m do\r\nh&#7885;c t&#7853;p ho&#7863;c c&ocirc;ng vi&#7879;c.<p></p></span></span></p><p style="margin:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:\r\ninter-ideograph;line-height:150%"><span class="textexposedshow"><span style=''font-size:13.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";\r\ncolor:#1D2129''>+ &#272;&#7889;i v&#7899;i xin visa du h&#7885;c D2, s&#7869; xem x&eacute;t c&#7845;p visa sau khi x&aacute;c\r\nminh v&#7899;i ch&iacute;nh quy&#7873;n &#273;&#7883;a ph&#4